smile-again-platform/
│
├── README.md                  ← Description of the project
├── package.json               ← Node.js project file (backend/frontend dependencies)
├── .gitignore                 ← Files to ignore by Git
├── firebase.json              ← Firebase settings if deploying to Firebase
├── .firebaserc                ← Firebase project config
│
├── public/                    ← Static files (favicon, index.html, etc.)
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── favicon.ico
│   └── assets/                ← Logo, Icons, etc.
│
├── src/                       ← Main frontend code
│   ├── App.js
│   ├── index.js
│   ├── styles/
│   │   └── main.css
│   ├── components/            ← UI Components
│   ├── pages/                 ← Pages (Home, Login, Register, etc.)
│   └── services/              ← API and helper services
│
├── backend/                   ← All backend logic
│   ├── server.js              ← Express.js or other backend entry
│   ├── routes/                ← Route handlers (API endpoints)
│   ├── controllers/           ← Business logic
│   ├── models/                ← Database models
│   └── middleware/            ← Security, auth, etc.
│
├── database/                  ← SQL or NoSQL setup/scripts
│   └── schema.sql or init.js
│
├── config/                    ← Firebase/Auth/Env config files
│   ├── firebaseConfig.js
│   └── appConfig.js
│
├── functions/ (optional)      ← Firebase Cloud Functions
│   ├── index.js
│   └── utils.js
│
└── test/                      ← Tests for backend/frontend
    ├── unit/
    └── integration/
